102
00:08:17,045 --> 00:08:19,034
Kami harus menyusuri semua jalan di Paris.

103
00:08:34,084 --> 00:08:37,045
Ketika pelanggan lain
menjadi tidak senang

104
00:08:37,045 --> 00:08:40,025
Menyebabkan
suasana restoran terlihat tidak nyaman..

105
00:08:42,075 --> 00:08:44,065
Helo.

106
00:08:47,095 --> 00:08:49,025
Selamat.

107
00:08:57,015 --> 00:08:58,065
Kau di sini.

108
